TopicTitle: New Parts made with .cfg file doesn't load correctly

Articles.Content:
Hi all,

I just started editing .cfg files to make custom parts and get a lower part count for my bigger projects. I only merged the stock 2x2 panels to create 8x8, 2x10 and more different ones.

Now, every time i built something in the VAB and want to load it later, the game can't load my file correctly and messes it up.

Building in the first place, makes no problems, only the reloading.

Here are some screenshots:

imgur link

and one .cfg file:

dropbox

Hope you can help me or have some suggestions.
Problem solved, had same file names for different parts. So changing the name fixed it.
